[[!meta title="Contact"]]

There are many ways to contact us, depending on the subject you want
to talk about.

Subscribe to mailing-lists
==========================

Those lists are public, subscribtion is open to anyone. Don't send
compromising information to them. Please respect the
[[code of conduct|contribute/working_together/code_of_conduct/]] when
interracting in Tails spaces.

tails-support
-------------

[[tails-support|support/tails-support]] is the mailing-list dedicated
to tails support. Subscribe if you have questions or if you want to
help by answering others :)

<form method="POST" action="https://mailman.boum.org/subscribe/tails-support">
	<input class="text" name="email" value=""/>
	<input class="button" type="submit" value="Subscribe"/>
</form>

