Contact
=======

tails-support-private
---------------------

You can write encrypted emails to <tails-support-private@boum.org> if
you need help that requires you to send compromising information. See
the [[OpenPGP key|doc/about/openpgp_keys#support]].

tails-press
-----------

If you're a journalist wanting to write about Tails, or if you want to
send us links to [[press articles|press]] about Tails, please write to
<tails-press@boum.org>.

tails-fundraising
-----------------

If you want to discuss funding, work contracts and such, please write
to <tails-fundraising@boum.org>.

tails-sysadmins
---------------

To talk about our infrastructure (servers, test suite, repositories,
mirrors...) please write to <tails-sysadmins@boum.org>.

tails-security
--------------

To warn us about vulnerabilities in Tails please write to
<tails-security@boum.org>.

tails
-----

For matters that are listed in none of the above, you can write
encrypted emails to <tails@boum.org>. See the
[[OpenPGP key|doc/about/openpgp_keys#index1h1]].

IRC
===

You can join our [[#tails and #tails-dev chatrooms|support/chat]];
note: only a few Tails core developers hang out there, so email is
preferred for anything that might be of interest for the larger Tails
development community.
